dc_title_s: Shoreline Changes - Legacy Historic Shorelines by Years: Maryland
dc_description_s: This is a MD iMAP hosted service layer. Find more information at http://imap.maryland.gov. Digital shoreline vectors derived from bromide or mylar copies of National Ocean Service T-sheets or hydrographic surveys. Area covered includes Chesapeake Bay and tidal tributary shorelines along the western side of the Chesapeake Bay and five 7. 5' quadrangles on the lower eastern shore of the Chesapeake Bay. Last Updated: 6/2017Map Service Layer Link: http://geodata. md. gov/imap/rest/services/Hydrology/MD_ShorelineChanges/MapServer/3
